1
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,320
Ai Wei.

2
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:50,220
Come in.

3
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,800
Is the circuit fixed?

4
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:52,460
It's fixed.

5
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:55,280
Why?

6
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,400
What smells so bad?

7
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,160
I'm selecting products.

8
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:58,840
Luosifen.

9
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,940
Have you eaten yet?

10
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,840
Not yet.

11
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:02,920
Perfect.

12
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,420
Help me taste this.

13
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,660
How can I help you taste it?

14
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,200
Have a taste.

15
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,860
Just try it.

16
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,000
See how you

17
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,199
feel after eating it.

18
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:21,880
This...

19
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:22,880
I really can't do this one.

20
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,280
This bowl smells too bad.

21
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,640
It smells bad but tastes good.

22
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,040
Alright then.

23
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,440
Then try the second bowl.

24
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:48,570
How is it?

25
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,960
The peanuts just aren't crunchy enough.

26
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,480
And

27
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,480
this one isn't as smelly as that one.

28
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,360
You've never even had luosifen.

29
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,040
Why are you so picky?

30
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,320
Try the third one.

31
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,000
Be careful.

32
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,130
It's a little spicy.

33
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,000
Are you okay?

34
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,120
Here,

35
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,050
have some water.

36
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,050
Feeling better?

37
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,000
You're out of alcohol.

38
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,660
Let me get you another bottle.

39
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,400
Why haven't you eaten your noodles?

40
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,659
They're all mushy now.

41
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,620
I'm not in the mood.

42
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:52,409
Still thinking about that beauty device?

43
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,040
Yeah.

44
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,680
The last time I saw Lulu,

45
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,280
she said that after graduation,

46
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,140
she wanted to be a beauty vlogger.

47
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,160
Now it's over.

48
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,960
It ruined her skin.

49
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,760
Do you think

50
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,160
there's something wrong with this device?

51
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,320
Probably not.

52
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,460
The product quality certification,

53
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,880
I saw it myself.

54
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,280
Regardless,

55
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,690
Lulu bought this device because of me.

56
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,770
I just feel really guilty about it.

57
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,160
All right.

58
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,960
It's not your fault.

59
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,720
Go to the company tomorrow

60
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,320
and ask Lu Li what's going on.

61
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,120
The noodles are mushy.

62
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,520
Let me make you a new bowl.

63
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,740
Where is Mr. Lu?

64
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,120
He's not here.

65
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,200
He went out this morning,

66
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:01,000
and didn't say when he'd be back.

67
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,140
I'll wait for him here.

68
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,740
You look terrible.

69
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:25,760
What's wrong?

70
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,120
Didn't sleep last night?

71
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,040
After such a huge incident,

72
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,040
how could I sleep?

73
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,680
That girl is my fan.

74
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,960
I went to the hospital to see her.

75
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,000
She's badly hurt.

76
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,440
What exactly is going on with this beauty device?

77
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,080
How did this happen?

78
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,080
Where is the problem?

79
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,840
And whose responsibility is it?

80
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,000
The company will handle everything.

81
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,760
You shouldn't have gone to see her alone.

82
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,640
She probably bought the beauty device because of me.

83
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,240
So what?

84
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,920
This beauty device

85
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:49,159
has FDA certification in the US

86
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,960
and CE certification in the EU.

87
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:53,490
They've sold hundreds of thousands of units.

88
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,840
Everyone else used it fine.

89
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,700
Why did only she have an accident?

90
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,760
Jiangzi.

91
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:03,920
As for this matter,

92
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,450
the company will handle it.

93
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,200
If it is the company's responsibility,

94
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:08,860
the company

95
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,740
will definitely not shirk it.

96
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,640
But if someone tries to scam us,

97
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,680
the company won't let them get away with it.

98
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:39,560
Mr. Li.

99
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,240
It's all over the internet.

100
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,170
What's going on?

101
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,320
I don't know about this either.

102
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,320
It was too sudden.

103
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,490
I've already had someone look into it.

104
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,760
Is there a problem with quality control?

105
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,960
Our quality control has always been strict.

106
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,560
And that beauty device

107
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,480
is legal and compliant.

108
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,210
All the licenses are complete.

109
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,400
But on the internet,

110
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,160
they are shifting the blame

111
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,400
onto Jiangzi and our Shengshi.

112
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,440
Did you know that?

113
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,000
Mr. Li.

114
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,800
Those people on the internet

115
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,160
just grab a target

116
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,960
and shoot their arrows desperately.

117
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:11,760
But don't worry.

118
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,480
Once I find out

119
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,240
any clues about this matter,

120
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,580
I will report to you immediately.

121
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:17,840
Hurry up.

122
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:40,960
Lulu.

123
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,240
How is it?

124
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,570
Did the surgery go well?

125
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,500
You don't need to be so hypocritical.

126
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,820
Why are you here again?

127
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,680
Don't think giving some stinking money

128
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,940
can solve the problem.

129
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:01,680
I'm telling you,

130
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:02,800
God is watching.

131
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,640
You're not welcome here.

132
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,120
Go.

133
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:04,680
Go.

134
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:05,010
Lulu.

135
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,980
These are my video stats for January.

136
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:13,760
Not bad.

137
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,240
I think so too.

138
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,120
You can go now.

139
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,900
Take a seat.

140
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,480
About the beauty device.

141
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,160
Did you pay Lulu hush money?

142
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,360
Yes.

143
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,000
Why?

144
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,240
So,

145
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:37,520
it wasn't her operational error at all.

146
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,320
It was the quality of the device.

147
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:42,080
Whose fault it is doesn't matter anymore.

148
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:42,960
What matters is that

149
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,360
this whole thing is over.

150
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,840
How does it not matter?

151
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,520
You paid Lulu off.

152
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,840
But what about the injury on her face?

153
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,900
Who's going to take responsibility?

154
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:51,650
Jiangzi,

155
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,000
are you blaming me now?

156
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:57,560
Right.

157
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:59,120
I did pay to keep her quiet.

158
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,480
But I did it all for you.

159
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,360
I can accept it if you're not grateful.

160
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,690
But how dare you come here and question me?

161
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,940
Do you have any idea

162
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,440
if this blows up,

163
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,330
what will happen to you?

164
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,520
Not to mention the Top Ten Influencer Award,

165
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,520
even your career would be over.

166
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,360
Don't think you can just lay low for a while

167
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,640
and make a comeback.

168
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,200
Look at Aiwei now.

169
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,440
Do you want to end up like her?

170
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:24,800
How can you be so self-righteous?

171
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,840
If we had done a good job with quality control,

172
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,560
this wouldn't have happened.

173
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,500
But it still happened, didn't it?

174
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,560
Her mother has already taken the money.

175
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,160
This matter is settled.

176
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,040
Holding someone accountable now

177
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,500
is completely pointless.

178
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:40,200
We have to look forward

179
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,800
to prevent things like this from happening again.

180
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,280
Okay?

181
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:49,240
The promo video for the beauty device must be taken down.

182
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:49,840
We can talk

183
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,000
about Lulu's matter later.

184
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,000
Don't you dare take it down.

185
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,760
Why?

186
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,080
If you take it down at this crucial moment,

187
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,080
what does it mean?

188
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,280
It means you have a guilty conscience

189
00:10:57,280 --> 00:10:58,000
and you're admitting to it.

190
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
Do you understand?

191
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,960
But the beauty device does have safety risks.

192
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,200
If the video doesn't get taken down,

193
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,280
more people will buy it,

194
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,320
and more will get hurt.

195
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,960
As for quality control,

196
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,600
I've had the manufacturer confirm it repeatedly.

197
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,280
This kind of thing won't happen again.

198
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:08,920
Even if it does,

199
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,200
it's highly unlikely,

200
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:10,840
you know?

201
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,120
Jiangzi.

202
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,160
You don't need to look at me like that.

203
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:16,960
Do you think

204
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:18,080
that by saying this,

205
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:18,720
I'm being really selfish

206
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,780
and cold-blooded?

207
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:21,960
But you need to understand one thing.

208
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,480
You are not alone right now.

209
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,640
You have a team.

210
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,840
The people outside,

211
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,100
from quality control,

212
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:28,640
editing,

213
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:29,160
planning,

214
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:29,890
to business,

215
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:32,160
they are all working just for you.

216
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,280
You want to smash your own rice bowl.

217
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,450
Do you want to smash theirs too?

218
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:43,560
Jiangzi.

219
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:45,960
I know.

220
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:46,640
That girl

221
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:49,080
bought that beauty device because of you.

222
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,560
And it is

223
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,360
because of you

224
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:53,410
that she suffered this injury.

225
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:55,080
You feel bad about it.

226
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,940
I completely understand.

227
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,560
But

228
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,280
I have to tell you,

229
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,600
in our industry,

230
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:03,420
things aren't so black and white.

231
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:05,520
Only by letting go of black and white

232
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,120
can we truly become popular.

233
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,160
Thank you.

234
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,680
When Aiwei ran into trouble before,

235
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,940
she'd also come here to space out.

236
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,600
Now you're just like her.

237
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,400
If when I took this ad,

238
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,160
I had done more research,

239
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,680
would this not have happened?

240
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,380
Don't think like that.

241
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:26,440
For something like this to happen,

242
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,480
no one wants it.

243
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:29,730
Besides,

244
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,960
the beauty device has safety risks.

245
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,420
It's also the manufacturer's fault.

246
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,360
You only sell it on your livestream.

247
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:40,420
You don't produce the beauty device.

248
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,400
But it's based on their trust in me

249
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:44,650
that fans buy what I recommend.

250
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:47,240
Since I reaped the benefits of their trust,

251
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:50,170
I should bear the corresponding responsibilities.

252
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,760
My mind is full

253
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:53,600
of Lulu's cute face right now.

254
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,000
She was so sunny,

255
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,120
cheerful,

256
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:00,680
and full of hope for life.

257
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:04,020
She trusted me unconditionally.

258
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:09,560
I ruined her.

259
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,680
I even ruined her life.

260
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:17,260
I understand how you feel.

261
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:19,880
But after all, Luli

262
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,640
has already spent money to settle this.

263
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:28,280
If you want to bear all the consequences yourself,

264
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,410
you need to know that

265
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:32,100
everything you've built,

266
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:33,680
your reputation,

267
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,840
your millions of fans...

268
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,770
will all be gone.

269
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,320
You alone

270
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,740
came all the way from Changde to Beijing.

271
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,560
You finally made it.

272
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,660
Are you going back empty-handed now?

273
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,480
If it were me,

274
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,880
I would definitely feel regret too.

275
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,800
If it were Aiwei,

276
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:03,960
what would she do?

277
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,410
I don't know either.

278
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,330
There are no ifs.

279
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:21,320
You can only be yourself.

280
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,000
I'm graduating soon,

281
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,240
and

282
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:08,200
I want to be a beauty blogger.

283
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:09,640
Look, Sis.

284
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,440
This is my portfolio.

285
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:12,760
These were all made

286
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:14,400
in the beauty blogger training class

287
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,160
by myself.

288
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,800
I don't need your hypocrisy.

289
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:27,420
Why are you here again?

290
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,280
Don't think giving some filthy money

291
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,540
can solve the problem.

292
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,280
Let me tell you.

293
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:34,400
Heaven is watching.

