00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,280
happy memories in our hearts?

588
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:03,720
Isn't that nice?

589
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:09,640
You...

590
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:12,210
Do you think there's something wrong with me?

591
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,640
I know sometimes I can be stubborn

592
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:15,560
and immature,

593
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:18,280
and I tend to throw little tantrums.

594
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:20,520
If you think I'm doing something wrong,

595
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:21,800
you can tell me.

596
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:22,880
I'll change.

597
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,560
I will.

598
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:25,680
I can change, okay?

599
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:26,840
Can you calm down?

600
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:28,480
Calm down.

601
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:32,320
Look.

602
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:35,010
You have your own charm.

603
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,360
I believe

604
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,160
you will definitely find a

605
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,160
better man than me

606
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:40,160
to be by your side.

607
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:43,570
You don't need to compromise yourself for me.

608
00:37:45,640 --> 00:37:46,900
And we are both adults.

609
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,280
If it works, we stay together;

610
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,360
if not, we part ways.

611
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,890
That's the rule of the game.

612
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:55,100
Promise me one last thing.

613
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,760
Let's break up amicably,

614
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,360
okay?

615
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,520
Lu Li.

616
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:08,000
I just want to ask you one thing.

617
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,800
Did you ever truly love me?

618
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:11,160
Were the things you said to me before

619
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:12,400
really true?

620
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:15,640
I think I made myself

621
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:17,000
very clear just now.

622
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:19,240
Lu Li.

623
00:38:20,040 --> 00:38:20,960
Answer me.

624
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:22,200
Answer me.

625
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,000
Say something!

626
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:30,920
Say something!

627
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,800
Say something!

628
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:33,240
Xiaoxiao.

629
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:33,520
Say something!

630
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:34,000
Xiaoxiao, you...

631
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,480
Have you had enough?

632
00:38:37,120 --> 00:38:38,580
Are you ever going to stop?

633
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:42,200
If I had known dumping you would be so troublesome,

634
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:44,660
I wouldn't have bothered in the first place.

635
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,850
You want to know the answer, right?

636
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:50,000
Fine, I can tell you.

637
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:54,200
I wanted to give you a decent breakup,

638
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:54,800
but

639
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,920
you had to tear away this facade.

640
00:38:57,880 --> 00:38:58,940
Then I'll tell you.

641
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:01,120
You asked me if I love you.

642
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:02,960
Did you think

643
00:39:03,680 --> 00:39:04,740
I made you a blogger

644
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:06,080
and bought you followers

645
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:07,610
because I really liked you?

646
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:09,480
To me,

647
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,240
you were just useful.

648
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:13,880
You were my tool to deal with Ai Wei.

649
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:15,920
If I didn't get close to you,

650
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,880
how could I get

651
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,200
so much dirt on Ai Wei?

652
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:19,600
How could I bring her down?

653
00:39:19,600 --> 00:39:21,000
Now that Ai Wei is ruined,

654
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,600
you are already

655
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:23,840
of no value to me.

656
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:25,480
I, Lu Li,

657
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:27,520
will not keep a worthless thing

658
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:28,880
by my side.

659
00:39:34,520 --> 00:39:35,120
Saying this now,

660
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,850
you should understand, right?

661
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:45,360
Oh, right.

662
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,160
The rent for this apartment

663
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:47,880
is paid until the end of the month.

664
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,080
Whether you stay or go

665
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:50,180
is up to you.

666
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:11,000
Hello, Dai.

667
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,480
What are you doing?

668
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:15,160
Why did it take you so long to answer?

669
00:42:15,160 --> 00:42:15,920
What do you think?

670
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:16,880
I'm busy.

671
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:17,800
Still busy?

672
00:42:19,240 --> 00:42:21,040
I'm telling you this seriously.

673
00:42:21,320 --> 00:42:22,400
Right now,

674
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:24,130
I'm drinking here in Sanlitun.

675
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,840
Two female colleagues came over.

676
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,100
They are quite pretty.

677
00:42:27,720 --> 00:42:28,360
Man,

678
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:31,040
I was thinking since you're single again.

679
00:42:31,680 --> 00:42:32,640
Hurry over here.

680
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,680
I'll introduce you to them.

681
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:36,400
Do I need you to introduce me?

682
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:39,560
Since I became single again,

683
00:42:39,560 --> 00:42:40,160
let me tell you,

684
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:40,920
the girls chasing me

685
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:43,120
are lining up from my house to Chang'an Avenue.

686
00:42:43,120 --> 00:42:43,480
Come on.

687
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,400
A girl even confessed to me yesterday.

688
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,760
She looks exactly like Lin Zhiling.

689
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:48,620
But I thought she had a bad temper,

690
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:50,210
so I turned her down.

691
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:51,100
How about that?

692
00:42:52,120 --> 00:42:52,980
I say, Jintian,

693
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:55,000
