694
00:42:55,000 --> 00:42:57,120
Don't I know what you are like?

695
00:42:57,120 --> 00:42:59,000
When have I ever bragged to you?

696
00:42:59,120 --> 00:42:59,640
You,

697
00:42:59,640 --> 00:43:00,720
stop worrying about me.

698
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:02,240
Worry about yourself.

699
00:43:02,760 --> 00:43:04,000
Alright, I'm not talking to you anymore.

700
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:04,330
Okay.

701
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:05,560
Talk to you later.

702
00:43:05,560 --> 00:43:05,800
Okay.

703
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:06,120
Bye.

704
00:43:42,600 --> 00:43:43,400
What's wrong?

705
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:44,960
Hello.

706
00:43:45,280 --> 00:43:46,880
Are you the owner's family?

707
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:50,560
Who are you?

708
00:43:51,440 --> 00:43:53,300
Why do you have Xiaoxiao's phone?

709
00:44:40,560 --> 00:44:41,640
How is Xiaoxiao?

710
00:44:46,160 --> 00:44:47,620
She's still in emergency.

711
00:45:33,800 --> 00:45:35,330
Doctor, how is the patient?

712
00:45:35,920 --> 00:45:37,280
We managed to save her life.

713
00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:38,140
She is fine now.

714
00:45:40,160 --> 00:45:41,960
Good thing she was found in time.

715
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:42,660
Otherwise,

716
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,280
it could have been fatal.

717
00:45:44,280 --> 00:45:45,240
Thank you, doctor.

718
00:45:45,240 --> 00:45:45,840
Thank you.

719
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:46,480
Thank you.

720
00:45:46,720 --> 00:45:47,200
It's nothing.

721
00:45:47,200 --> 00:45:47,930
It's my duty.

722
00:45:48,280 --> 00:45:49,140
Just wait here.

723
00:45:49,360 --> 00:45:50,440
After the observation,

724
00:45:50,440 --> 00:45:50,960
she will be sent to the ward.

725
00:45:50,960 --> 00:45:51,520
Thank you.

726
00:45:51,520 --> 00:45:51,850
Okay.

727
00:45:52,440 --> 00:45:53,040
Thank you.

728
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:07,640
Jiangzi

729
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:07,400
Ai Wei

730
00:46:07,640 --> 00:46:07,920
Luo Xin

731
